                                            ReactJS application


--> Components, state, props.
--> Presentational component, functional component, container component.
--> UI routing.
--> Redux actions, thunk, logger, middleware.
--> Controlled and un-controlled forms.
--> client-server side communication, fetch().
--> react animations.

--> localhost:3001 (server side web data)
--> localhost:3000 (client side data)


                                         Steps to execute application
                                        
 I implemented the whole project using visual studio text editor, so giving out the same steps to execute the application:
 --->  Make a local directory and git clone https://github.com/trshinde/reactApp.git to that directory.
 --->  cd 
